Class TrendDaoImplTest

java.lang.Object
com.wileyedge.fashiontrendanalysis.dao.TrendDaoImplTest
@ExtendWith(org.mockito.junit.jupiter.MockitoExtension.class) public class TrendDaoImplTest extends Object
Test class for the TrendDaoImpl. It tests various CRUD operations related to the Trend entity.
